TITLE: Configuring Hierarchical Facets in Algolia Helper
DESCRIPTION: Sets up hierarchical facets for creating nested navigation menus. It defines the facet structure and demonstrates how to refine search based on hierarchical selections.
SOURCE: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/blob/master/packages/algoliasearch-helper/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
var helper = algoliasearchHelper(client, indexName, {
  hierarchicalFacets: [
    {
      name: 'products',
      attributes: ['categories.lvl0', 'categories.lvl1'],
    },
  ],
});
```

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
helper.toggleFacetRefinement('products', 'fruits > citrus');
```

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
helper.on('result', function (event) {
  console.log(event.results.hierarchicalFacets[0]);
  // {
  //   'name': 'products',
  //   'count': null,
