TITLE: Displaying Formatted Search Results in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Updates the result rendering function to extract and display the name field from each hit. This creates a more focused view of search results compared to displaying the entire JSON response.
SOURCE: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/blob/master/packages/algoliasearch-helper/documentation-src/content/gettingstarted.md#2025-04-17_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
