TITLE: Initializing and Configuring an InstantSearch Widget
DESCRIPTION: Code example showing how to import, initialize, and configure an InstantSearch widget with Algolia search client. This demonstrates the basic setup process for adding a custom widget to InstantSearch.
SOURCE: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/blob/master/packages/create-instantsearch-app/src/templates/InstantSearch.js widget/README.md#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import instantsearch from 'instantsearch.js';
import algoliasearch from 'algoliasearch/lite';
import { {{ camelCaseName }} } from '{{ packageName }}';

const searchClient = algoliasearch('appId', 'apiKey');

const search = instantsearch({
  indexName: 'indexName',
  searchClient,
});

search.addWidgets([
  {{ camelCaseName }}({
    // widget parameters
  }),
]);

search.start();
```

