TITLE: Using Disjunctive Facet Refinements in Algolia JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of adding multiple disjunctive facet refinements, which combines filters using OR logic. This example shows filtering TVs to include those with either CRT, LED, or plasma technology.
SOURCE: https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/blob/master/packages/algoliasearch-helper/documentation-src/content/reference.md#2025-04-17_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// helper is already configured
helper.addDisjunctiveFacetRefinement('tech', 'crt');
helper.addDisjunctiveFacetRefinement('tech', 'led');
helper.addDisjunctiveFacetRefinement('tech', 'plasma');

// the filters are equals to
// tech = crt OR tech = led OR tech = plasma
```

